'''卡普空温哥华'''（{{lang|en|Capcom Vancouver}}，前称“'''Blue Castle Games'''”）是一家位于加拿大的电子游戏开发商。公司以“Blue Castle Games”之名成立于2005年，并制作了一系列以[[美国职业棒球大联盟|美国职业棒球大联盟]]为主题的电子游戏。2010年，其开发的《[[丧尸围城2|丧尸围城2]]》发售，同年被[[卡普空|卡普空]]收购并更名为“卡普空温哥华（Capcom Vancouver）”。<ref name="announcement">{{cite web| url= http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=285199| title= Blue Castle making Dead Rising 2| date= 2008-11-07| author= Johnny Minkley| accessdate= 2016-07-17| archive-date= 2008-12-16| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20081216092912/http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=285199| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="kotaku dr2 rumor">{{cite web|title=Dead Rising 2: Dead Rising 2 Set in Vegas?|url=http://kotaku.com/5023576/dead-rising-2-set-in-vegas-|publisher=Kotaku|author=Brian Crecente|date=2008-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-17|archive-date=2016-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730182148/http://kotaku.com/5023576/dead-rising-2-set-in-vegas-|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="games_in_development">{{cite web|url = http://www.bluecastlegames.com/#pageId,14|title = Blue Castle Games - Games under development|accessdate = 2008-09-10|publisher = Blue Castle Games|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080909032506/http://www.bluecastlegames.com/#pageId,14|archivedate = 2008-09-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.develop-online.net/news/35862/Capcom-buys-Blue-Castle-Games|title=Capcom buys Blue Castle Games|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111215111236/http://www.develop-online.net/news/35862/Capcom-buys-Blue-Castle-Games|archivedate=2011年12月15日|df=|accessdate=2016年7月17日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/news/capcom-buys-dead-rising-2-dev-blue-castle-games|title=Capcom Buys Dead Rising 2 Dev Blue Castle Games|accessdate=2016-07-17|archive-date=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531112410/http://www.edge-online.com/news/capcom-buys-dead-rising-2-dev-blue-castle-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>公司还与[[微软工作室|微软工作室]]有稳定的合作。2018年9月，卡普空宣布停止卡普空温哥华手上的新游戏的开发，并在之后宣布关闭工作室。<ref>[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/capcom-shutters-dead-rising-studio-capcom-vancouve/1100-6461846/ Capcom Shutters Dead Rising Studio, Capcom Vancouver] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/capcom-shutters-dead-rising-studio-capcom-vancouve/1100-6461846/ |date=20180927125246 }}.Gamespot.2018-09-21.[2018-09-27].</ref>

